  "detailed_description": "Avoid everything, touch nothing, and reach a screen edge!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751720/extras/b0a92be045ac5a509bb6cd40819fd568.poster.avif?t=1729459467\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751720/extras/b0a92be045ac5a509bb6cd40819fd568.webm?t=1729459467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751720/extras/b0a92be045ac5a509bb6cd40819fd568.mp4?t=1729459467\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Project Ictos is a fast-paced game with difficult levels that are simple on the surface, but hard to learn and master.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Multiple game modes!<br></li><li> A practice mode to improve your skills!<br></li><li> Lots of achievements!<br></li><li> A soundtrack that is tied to the game's progress!</li></ul>",
